\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 you to the research screen, where you can select new technologies }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 to discover and allocate teams of scientists to accomplish this as }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 quickly as possible.}{
