#{\footnote Hlp_Overview}
${\footnote Introduction}
K{\footnote Overview}
+{\footnote final:0010}

\ql\li0\fi0\ri-26656{\f0\fs48\cf1\up0\dn0 Introduction}{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-26656{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-26656{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 4000 A.D. is a variation on the familiar 4X strategy game - eXplore, }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 eXpand, eXploit and eXterminate.  By spreading your empire }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 across the galaxy, maximizing resource production and }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 researching new technologies, you can try to crush your enemy }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 and take your rightful place as ruler of the known universe.}{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-26656{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-26656{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 The game is turn-based, with each player completing their turn and }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 emailing the resulting file to their opponent.  Besides a copy of this }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 program, you will need access to internet email to send turns back }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 and forth.  Hot-seat play is also possible, but not the best way to }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 spend an evening.  The game was designed so that a turn can be }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 completed and emailed within 5-10 minutes.  Why? So you can }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 play it at work without being fired, and because most people don't }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 have 3-5 hours at a time for the more intensive strategy games out }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 there (Starcraft, Total Annihiliation, Age of Empires etc.).  I know I }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 don't.}{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-26656{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-26656{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 At the start of each new game, the planets are re-initialized with a }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 random level of resource production, so no two games will have the }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 same distribution of resources.}{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-26656{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-26656{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 Gameplay is open-ended with the players deciding when the game }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 ends, by total conquest or humiliating surrender.}{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-26656{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql{\f0\fs18\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql{\f0\fs18\cf0\up0\dn0
