\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-26656{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 You may choose one of three sizes of galaxy, which will affect the }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 number of troops and resources you start the game out with.  }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 Beginners should select either the large (50 planets) or medium (40 }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 planets) galaxy, as the small size (30 planets) is more of a }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 challenge with respect to resource management.}{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-26656{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
