\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\f0\fs48\cf1\up0\dn0 Sabotage Missions}{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\b\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\b\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 Launching the Mission:}{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 After selecting a ship to launch from the launch screen, click on the 'sabotage }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 mission' checkbox. This will automatically prepare the ship for a sabotage }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 mission, which requires only 1 mech to carry out (you must have at least 1 mech }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 on the planet to operate the ship).}{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 If you have researched the {\ul Cloaking Device}{\v Cloaking_Device } you may check that box as well to }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 maintain the element of surprise.  When you land the ship on an enemy planet }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 you will be notified as to the mission's success (or failure, depending on the level }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 of the planet's defenses), and the damage done to the planet's resource }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 production.  The success of the mission may be threatened by a number of }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 factors, including the planet's population and whether any missile bases or }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 scanners have been installed.}{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 Ships on sabotage missions are marked with an "S" on your warp path, but your }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 opponent will not see this identifier.}{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\b\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 {\ul Repairing Industry}{\v Repairing_Industry }}{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 :  }{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 If any of your planets have been sabotaged and their resource production falls }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 below 4 units/turn, you can rebuild your basic industrial facilities.  If you had }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 already built an Advanced Resource Production Facility, it will have been }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 destroyed by the saboteurs and must be rebuilt.}{
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql\li0\fi0\ri-28096{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 *Note: you should repair your industries as much as possible before building }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 another Advanced Resource Production Facility, as the Facility improves }
\ql{\f0\fs24\cf0\up0\dn0 resource production as a percentage of the planet's current resource production.}{
\par}\pard
\ql{\f0\fs18\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql{\f0\fs18\cf0\up0\dn0
\par}\pard
\ql{\f0\fs18\cf0\up0\dn0 Helpfile generated by VB HelpWriter.}{
